questions: What are the expected properties for a given query and category?
What type of data is expected for the "query" property?
What is an example of a valid value for the "category" property?
answer:
## Expected properties. 
!!! Tip

    All properties are optional. If any property is missing it will not be processed and no error will be reported.
    
| Name     | Expected type   | Example                                         |
|----------|-----------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| query    | string          | "Contact page"    |
| category | string          | "Search" |
